Run this program to check whether the signature is authentic or not.
This folder has 2 program files Ass2.py and generate.py.
Run generate.py to create signatures using private key(private.pem).
Use Ass2.py to check the authenticity of a signature using public key(public.pub)

To run files use:

python filename

Example of valid pairs:

text : kanpur
signature : 


text : computer
signature :


text : laptop
signature :


Examples of invalid pairs:

text : hello
signature :


text : high
signature :


NOTE : private.pem should be in the same folder as generate.py
